(23, 'Pope Francis arrives in Indonesia to begin historic Asia tour', 8, 10, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/pope-francis\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Pope Francis</a>&nbsp;arrived in Muslim-majority&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/indonesia\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Indonesia</a>&nbsp;on Tuesday,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/pope-francis-asia-china-indonesia-b2605718.html\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">kicking off a 12-day marathon visit</a>&nbsp;focused on interfaith dialogue.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Francis landed in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/jakarta\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Jakarta</a>&nbsp;after a 13-hour flight from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/rome\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Rome</a>&nbsp;and disembarked in his wheelchair. He received a warm welcome by officials, including the religious affairs minister, a traditional bouquet from two children, and a guard of honour.</font></p><div id=\"article-im-prompt\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The leader of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/ap-indonesia-catholics-flores-christ-b2604842.html\" title=\"Catholics face a shortage of priests. But one Indonesian seminary is overwhelmed with applicants\" style=\"color: rgb(172, 42, 44);\">worldâ€™s 1.3 billion Catholics&nbsp;</a>will spend three nights in Jakarta. He will formally begin his tour on Wednesday with a full day of activities planned in the capital.