 color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">President Joko Widodo welcomed Pope Francis saying Indonesia and the Vatican â€œhave the same commitment to fostering peace and brotherhood, as well as ensuring the welfare of humanityâ€.</font></p>', '2024-09-03 13:22:07', '2024-09-03 14:01:00', 1, 'Pope-Francis-arrives-in-Indonesia-to-begin-historic-Asia-tour', '8a99c208af6f3ee444316f4f9269543d.jpg'),
