(31, 'Gus Atkinson makes history in triple-feat summer at Lordâ€™s', 9, 11, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/cricket/chris-woakes-england-jason-holder-mark-wood-west-indies-b2586676.html\" title=\"Chris Woakes says newcomer Gus Atkinson making Test cricket look â€˜quite easyâ€™\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Gus Atkinson ensured that his name&nbsp;</a>would be on three honours boards at the home of cricket when he scored his maiden Test century in sparkling against Sri Lanka at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/lords\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Lordâ€™s</a>.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/cricket/joe-root-ollie-pope-england-sri-lanka-fernando-b2604061.html\" title=\"Joe Root equals England record with crucial century against Sri Lanka\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Atkinson started the second day at Lordâ€™s unbeaten</a>&nbsp;on 74 from just 81 deliveries, playing positively but well for his chanceless innings, and carried on in exactly the same fashion, showing very few nerves.</font></p><div id=\"article-im-prompt\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/cricket/james-anderson-england-west-indies-jimmy-surrey-b2577462.html\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Having burst onto the international scene at the start of the summer,</a>&nbsp;taking 12 wickets including a five-wicket haul in his first Test match, which was also&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/james-anderson\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">James Anderson</a>â€™s last, he has now added a century. Atkinsonâ€™s triple figures came at an impressive run a ball including 11 fours and four sixes.</font></p><div class=\"sc-w27hnf-3 glAnFg desktop-only teads\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"sc-1y9ieyw-0 fZKFoR\" style=\"position: relative; max-width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin: 0px auto; background-color: transparent; clear: both;\"><div class=\"sc-1pfx6hk-0 kBYRNf\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><div data-mpu=\"true\" data-is-video=\"false\" data-tile-name=\"thirdparty01\" data-ad-unit-path=\"/71347885/_partner_independent/in_sport/in_cricket/image/thirdparty01\" data-size-key=\"THIRD_PARTY_ARTICLE_BODY_DESKTOP\" data-refresh-check=\"false\" data-refresh-ms=\"150000\"></div></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Atkinsonâ€™s hundred saw him become only the sixth player to hit a century, take five wickets in an innings and take 10 wickets in a match at Lordâ€™s. He was eventually out for 118 when he was caught on the boundary, and given a standing ovation as he left the field.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The intent was evident from the first ball of the day, when he clipped Lahiru Kumara away for four, and followed it up with a second boundary through the covers.</font></p>', '2024-09-03 23:13:17', NULL, 1, 'Gus-Atkinson-makes-history-in-triple-feat-summer-at-Lordâ€™s', '7166985526783a167f385d59c8dd26fe.jpg'),
(32, 'Jonnie Peacock calls for Seb Coe to include para-athletics in Diamond League', 9, 20, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\"><a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/jonnie-peacock\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Jonnie Peacock</a>&nbsp;sank to fifth at the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/paralympics\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Paralympics</a>&nbsp;but did not miss his opportunity to call out&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/seb-coe\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Seb Coe</a>&nbsp;and demand genuine inclusion in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/diamond-league\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Diamond League</a>&nbsp;programme.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Disability disciplines are included by host cities of Diamond League events on a discretionary basis, with classifications often combined and events taking place outside of the global broadcast window.</font></p><div id=\"article-im-prompt\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Para athletics is governed by the International Paralympic Committee, not&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/world-athletics\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">World Athletics</a>, but Peacock used his platform at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/paris-2024\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Paris 2024</a>&nbsp;to insist that Coe intervenes.</font></p><div class=\"sc-w27hnf-3 glAnFg desktop-only teads\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"sc-1y9ieyw-0 fZKFoR\" style=\"position: relative; max-width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin: 0px auto; background-color: transparent; clear: both;\"><div class=\"sc-1pfx6hk-0 kBYRNf\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><div data-mpu=\"true\" data-is-video=\"false\" data-tile-name=\"thirdparty01\" data-ad-unit-path=\"/71347885/_partner_independent/in_sport/in_olympics/image/thirdparty01\" data-size-key=\"THIRD_PARTY_ARTICLE_BODY_DESKTOP\" data-refresh-check=\"false\" data-refresh-ms=\"150000\"></div></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œThe Paralympics, we need to stop letting it die,â€ said Peacock, who is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sportâ€™s National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the worldâ€™s best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support â€“ which has been vital on their pathway to the Paris 2024 Games.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œSeb Coe, I need you, we need you, to put us in the actual Diamond League. Not a cheerleader event, not five minutes before the cameras turn on, we need to be visible.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"></p>', '2024-09-03 23:26:20', NULL, 1, 'Jonnie-Peacock-calls-for-Seb-Coe-to-include-para-athletics-in-Diamond-League', '1f02adbb7c2433a8a76d5c8a718bcae5.jpg'),
(33, 'Britainâ€™s Natasha Baker: Para dressage horses treated like kings and queens', 9, 20, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Natasha Baker insisted para equestrian horses are â€œtreated like kings and queensâ€ and the whipping scandal is not representative of all riders after winning bronze at Paris 2024.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Equine welfare came under the microscope ahead of the Olympics when three-time gold medallist&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/charlotte-dujardin\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Charlotte Dujardin</a>&nbsp;was suspended due to footage emerging of her repeatedly whipping a horse.</font></p><div id=\"article-im-prompt\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Baker clinched third place on the podium in the grade three individual event on Tuesday as Paralympic dressage events began at Chateau de Versailles, before British teammate Georgia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/wilson\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Wilson</a>&nbsp;replicated that feat in grade two.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The six-time gold medallist, who was riding Keystone Dawn Chorus â€“ also known as Lottie, said: â€œWe love our horses so, so, so much. Especially in para dressage, we are trusting our horses with our entire life.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œI am pretty useless physically and so I am putting all of my trust into Lottie and she, I think, loves me as much as I love her, and I think thatâ€™s really on display.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œIâ€™d love to invite anybody to my yard and at any time. I think these horses are treated like kings and queens.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œJust because one situation has happened doesnâ€™t mean weâ€™re all doing the same.â€</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Baker posted a score of 73.167 on a grey morning in the grounds of the former royal residence commissioned by King&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/louis-xiv\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Louis XIV</a>&nbsp;to win the ninth medal of a Paralympic career which began at London 2012.</font></p><div class=\"sc-toncsa-0 jQFbah\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The 34-year-old became a mother in May last year and spent 12 months out of the saddle.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">She blew a kiss to son Joshua after performing in heavy rain before likening her horse to fictional nanny Mary Poppins.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œIf youâ€™d told me that I was going to even be selected for the Paris Games over Christmas, I would have absolutely laughed in your face,â€ said Baker, who finished behind&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/topic/american\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">American</a>&nbsp;Rebecca Hart and Rixt van der Horst of the Netherlands.</font></p>', '2024-09-03 23:28:11', NULL, 1, 'Britainâ€™s-Natasha-Baker:-Para-dressage-horses-treated-like-kings-and-queens', '6c96a543e172640c849b698e491d6465.jpg'),
(34, 'Google Pixel 9 is available to buy now - plus pre-order Pro and Fold', 12, 17, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Google officially revealed the new Pixel 9 series of phones at its annual Made by Google event in Mountain View, California.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" data-affiliate=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/esimedia_t58ukgmjkf95_theindependent?q=http%3A%2F%2Fgo.redirectingat.com%2F%3Fid%3D44681X1458326%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstore.google.com%252Fgb%252Fproduct%252Fpixel_9%253Fhl%253Den-GB%26sref%3D%2Fextras%2Findybest%2Fgadgets-tech%2Fphones-accessories%2Fgoogle-pixel-9-buy-now-b2600073.html&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fextras%2Findybest%2Fgadgets-tech%2Fphones-accessories%2Fgoogle-pixel-9-buy-now-b2600073.html&amp;article_id=2600073&amp;author=Steve+Hogarty&amp;tag=indybest%2CGoogle&amp;section=IndyBest&amp;category=Tech&amp;sub_category=Phones+%26+Accessories&amp;updated_time=2024-08-22T10%3A21%3A06.000Z&amp;utm_campaign=news-body&amp;utm_term=B-1&amp;utm_content=&amp;utm_medium=desktop&amp;ref=www.independent.co.uk&amp;utm_source=independent&amp;fbclid=&amp;gclid=\" style=\"color: rgb(236, 26, 46);\">Pixel 9</a>&nbsp;starts from Â£799, the&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" data-affiliate=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/esimedia_t58ukgmjkf95_theindependent?q=http%3A%2F%2Fgo.redirectingat.com%2F%3Fid%3D44681X1458326%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstore.google.com%252Fgb%252Fproduct%252Fpixel_9_pro%253Fhl%253Den-GB%26sref%3D%2Fextras%2Findybest%2Fgadgets-tech%2Fphones-accessories%2Fgoogle-pixel-9-buy-now-b2600073.html&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fextras%2Findybest%2Fgadgets-tech%2Fphones-accessories%2Fgoog