(44, 'One dead after Royal Navy Merlin helicopter ditches in the Channel', 8, 10, '<p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">A member of Royal Navy personnel has died after a Merlin helicopter plunged into the English Channel.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The Merlin Mk4 helicopter, favoured by Royal Marines for rapid deployment, ditched during a night flying exercise with HMS&nbsp;<em>Queen Elizabeth</em>&nbsp;off the Dorset coast on Wednesday night.</font></p><div id=\"article-im-prompt\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">It is understood three crew members were on board the helicopter when it entered the water. Two were rescued and were taken to hospital without suffering serious injuries.</font></p><div class=\"sc-w27hnf-3 iOJCvF desktop-only teads\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"sc-1y9ieyw-0 joBdHo\" style=\"position: relative; max-width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin: 0px auto; background-color: transparent; clear: both;\"><div class=\"sc-1pfx6hk-0 lgUbTS\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><div data-mpu=\"true\" data-is-video=\"false\" data-tile-name=\"thirdparty01\" data-ad-unit-path=\"/71347885/_partner_independent/in_news/in_uk/video/thirdparty01\" data-size-key=\"THIRD_PARTY_ARTICLE_BODY_DESKTOP\" data-refresh-check=\"false\" data-refresh-ms=\"150000\"></div></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The third personâ€™s body has been recovered but they have not yet been named.</font></p><div class=\"sc-482ou5-2 eOHevC image align-none\" style=\"position: relative; margin: 0px 0px 16px; clear: both; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><figure class=\"sc-1cbdeug-0 cpcmmN\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div data-gallery-length=\"4\" class=\"sc-482ou5-0 fdNrAo\" style=\"display: grid; position: relative; aspect-ratio: 6849 / 4568;\"><img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/CHF-20230530-XD0030-006.jpg\" srcset=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/CHF-20230530-XD0030-006.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;auto=webp 320w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/CHF-20230530-XD0030-006.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=640&amp;auto=webp 640w\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Merlin of 751 Esquadra, top, and a Merlin Mk 4, bottom, flying over Lisbon\" class=\"sc-1mc30lb-0 iSVhwZ inline-gallery-btn\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-gallery-length=\"4\" style=\"width: 624px; height: 416.312px; display: block; object-fit: cover; grid-area: 1 / 1 / 2 / 2;\"></div><figcaption class=\"sc-1cbdeug-1 sc-1cbdeug-3 hiCdLa liXvvg\" style=\"color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; padding: 8px 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Merlin of 751 Esquadra, top, and a Merlin Mk 4, bottom, flying over Lisbon<span class=\"sc-1cbdeug-7 izyooE\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;(Royal Navy)</span></font></figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">In a statement, the Royal Navy said: â€œIt is with great sadness that we must report a member of the Royal Navy has died following a training incident last night.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œOur thoughts are with the family â€“ who have been informed â€“ and all those affected at this sad time. A full investigation will take place.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">â€œThe incident involved a Merlin Mk4 helicopter in the English Channel near Dorset that ditched while conducting night flying exercises with HMS&nbsp;<em>Queen Elizabeth</em>. There were no other fatalities or serious injuries.â€</font></p><div class=\"sc-toncsa-0 gdPcRA\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The UK Civil Aviation Authority describes ditching as â€œa deliberate emergency landing on waterâ€, rather than a crash, in a guidance document from 2022.</font></p><div class=\"sc-482ou5-2 eOHevC image align-none\" style=\"position: relative; margin: 0px 0px 16px; clear: both; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><figure class=\"sc-1cbdeug-0 cpcmmN\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div data-gallery-length=\"4\" class=\"sc-482ou5-0 eMYPKO\" style=\"display: grid; position: relative; aspect-ratio: 6000 / 4000;\"><img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/03/21/17/60628d8218fe1fe7826cbe6999a078fcY29udGVudHNlYXJjaGFwaSwxNzExMTI3OTEx-2.75656951.jpg\" srcset=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/03/21/17/60628d8218fe1fe7826cbe6999a078fcY29udGVudHNlYXJjaGFwaSwxNzExMTI3OTEx-2.75656951.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;auto=webp 320w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/03/21/17/60628d8218fe1fe7826cbe6999a078fcY29udGVudHNlYXJjaGFwaSwxNzExMTI3OTEx-2.75656951.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=640&amp;auto=webp 640w\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"The helicopter was taking part in a night training exercise alongside â€˜HMS Queen Elizabethâ€™\" class=\"sc-1mc30lb-0 iSVhwZ inline-gallery-btn\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-gallery-length=\"4\" style=\"width: 624px; height: 416.312px; display: block; object-fit: cover; grid-area: 1 / 1 / 2 / 2;\"></div><figcaption class=\"sc-1cbdeug-1 sc-1cbdeug-3 hiCdLa liXvvg\" style=\"color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; padding: 8px 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The helicopter was taking part in a night training exercise alongside â€˜HMS Queen Elizabethâ€™<span class=\"sc-1cbdeug-7 izyooE\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;(PA Wire)</span></font></figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Prime minister Sir Keir Starmer said he was â€œdeeply saddenedâ€ by the death.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">In a post on X, he added: â€œMy thoughts are with the family and loved ones during this painful time.â€</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Sir Keir paid tribute to the shipâ€™s company â€œparticularly those involved in the search-and-rescue operationâ€.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Defence secretary John Healey described the news of the death as â€œtruly dreadfulâ€ and promised â€œa full investigationâ€ into how the fatal accident happened.</font></p><div class=\"sc-482ou5-2 eOHevC image align-none\" style=\"position: relative; margin: 0px 0px 16px; clear: both; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><figure class=\"sc-1cbdeug-0 cpcmmN\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div data-gallery-length=\"4\" class=\"sc-482ou5-0 eMYPKO\" style=\"display: grid; position: relative; aspect-ratio: 6000 / 4000;\"><img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/6913c8ba-81fb-40e5-898b-336e75e6c42a.jpg\" srcset=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/6913c8ba-81fb-40e5-898b-336e75e6c42a.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=320&amp;auto=webp 320w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2024/09/05/15/6913c8ba-81fb-40e5-898b-336e75e6c42a.jpg?quality=75&amp;width=640&amp;auto=webp 640w\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Defence secretary John Healey offered his condolences\" class=\"sc-1mc30lb-0 iSVhwZ inline-gallery-btn\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-gallery-length=\"4\" style=\"width: 624px; height: 416.312px; display: block; object-fit: cover; grid-area: 1 / 1 / 2 / 2;\"></div><figcaption class=\"sc-1cbdeug-1 sc-1cbdeug-3 hiCdLa liXvvg\" style=\"color: rgb(100, 100, 100); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; padding: 8px 16px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Defence secretary John Healey offered his condolences<span class=\"sc-1cbdeug-7 izyooE\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;(Ben Birchall/PA Wire)</span></font></figcaption></figure></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">While on a visit to HMS<em>&nbsp;Diamond</em>&nbsp;in Portsmouth, he told reporters: â€œI use dreadful because this is what everyone connected to the armed forces [dreads], news of personnel in service dying and all my thoughts and the thoughts of those in the wider navy Iâ€™ve been with today are with the family, the friends and the close colleagues of the one weâ€™ve lost today.â€</font></p><div class=\"sc-w27hnf-3 iOJCvF teads\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"sc-1y9ieyw-0 joBdHo\" style=\"position: relative; max-width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin: 0px auto; background-color: transparent; clear: both;\"><div class=\"sc-1pfx6hk-0 lgUbTS\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><div data-mpu=\"true\" data-is-video=\"false\" data-tile-name=\"thirdparty02\" data-ad-unit-path=\"/71347885/_partner_independent/in_news/in_uk/video/thirdparty02\" data-size-key=\"THIRD_PARTY_ARTICLE_BODY\" data-refresh-check=\"false\" data-refresh-ms=\"150000\"></div></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">The recently upgraded Mk4 helicopter features several modifications for use by the Royal Marines like a fast roping beam for the rapid deployment of special forces from the main cabin door.</font></p><p style=\"font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.44em; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">Navy Lookout reports the Mk4 has an exceptional safety record, with the last accident being a heavy landing at Camp Bastion, Afghanistan in 2010 while in RAF service.</font></p>', '2024-09-05 23:11:07', '2024-09-05 23:11:51', 1, 'One-dead-after-Royal-Navy-Merlin-helicopter-ditches-in-the-Channel', 'efc61dc73c8178ec03b7e136ae4d0efa.jpg');

